<plot>An elderly man grieving at the recent loss of his wife returns to his former University in search of a time capsule buried in the grounds 50 years earlier. However, the beautiful Ginkgo trees are the only things remaining as he is forced to confront the gulf between the memories he has been living on and the reality of modern change.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?629272</url></doc>
